This caused an "unspecified launch failure" on older hardware without
Unified Memory. (With Unified Memory, the host array is silently copied
to the GPU). The commit fixes this error.

The bug was detected by automatic testing, e.g.:
http://my.cdash.org/testDetails.php?test=27984534&build=1066464
http://my.cdash.org/testDetails.php?test=28240093&build=1074683
---
